			<li><div class="container"><div class="column left"><h2><span style="color: #fff200;">Who we are</span></h2>
<p>The Globe is a creative collaboration with a foundational belief in the power of effective branding and design. We build brands and amplify them across a diverse range of media. Our approach is driven by strategic and creative opportunities to yield a unifying and consistently executed message. Passion for our craft drives us to pursue compelling outcomes for our clients—because we love what we&#8217;re doing and, as we ply our craft, our clients grow.</p>
</div><div class="column middle"><h2><span style="color: #fff200;">Process</span></h2>
<p>Our process is intentional and considered, yet we don&#8217;t don it as a straightjacket (it makes it far too hard to use your arms). We begin with understanding: of our client, of their competitive environment, and of the unique challenges and opportunities they&#8217;re facing. Client relationships fuel the building of a brand and a business—they also make work a whole lot more enjoyable. Tomorrow&#8217;s a brand new day!</p>
